<paragraph blockId="21.[826,1441,1312,1548]" pageId="21" pageNumber="50">Evaporative area short, distance from dorsal margin of auricle to dorsal margin of evaporative area shorter than distance from dorsal margin of evaporative area to dorsal margin of metapleura; posterior half of hemelytra darkened, with a subquadrangular whitish spot on apical region of corium and apex of membrane. Labium long, extending to or surpassing metacoxae.</paragraph>
